{"tid":1198900,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"致各位琴日遊完行早走 之後係ig po story怨政府嘅人","createTime":"2019-06-10T10:53:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-10T17:17:12.000Z","uid":15933,"like":33,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6315282bf52545517d64b72fa0986f3fef63c371","tid":1198900,"uid":15933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T10:53:45.000Z","msg":"我想講嘅係<br />\n留定唔留係你自己嘅選擇 如果自己都冇盡力去維護同捍衛自己嘅家園 咁唔該你唔好係呢啲社交平台到怨政府  明知呢個政府係咁強硬 蠻不講理嘅時候<br />\n100萬人上去都唔理 唔通係到怨幾句佢就會聽你講？<br />\n<br />\n我見到好多走咗嘅人 之後嘅節目都po 自己去睇戲<br />\n飲茶 乜乜乜  我當堂真係o撚咗 念力抗爭呀宜家<br />\n<br />\n我明白 琴日嘅形勢係好亂 就算留咗係到都唔知自己做緊乜 學生 有一家大細  大肚婆 走嘅 我明白<br />\n <br />\n但我想講 其實琴晚衝去前線嘅人 我相信佢地唔係冇自己嘢要做 佢地都唔係輸到冇嘢好輸  佢地都有工要返 有屋企人要照顧 有好多顧慮<br />\n但佢地義無反顧咁衝 係真係一心係為香港 同為政府嘅判決做出最有力嘅反抗 <br />\n好多後生仔  又或者係女仔 短衫短褲 矮矮細細都好 佢地琴日都衝咗上前 又或者係幫手救援<br />\n我相信衝得出嚟嘅人 佢地係大是大非前選擇為公眾利益爭取而非個人利益 <br />\n<br />\n係香港最後危急關頭 就算有警察 出咗幾多防暴 照衝 因為大家都怕自己錯過最後機會要抗爭<br />\n<br />\n所以<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">我唔係咩大人物 我只係一普通小市民打工仔 但我懇請大家 我求下大家 11號晚 12號 出嚟 推翻鐵血暴政 切勿錯過任何有得出嚟抗爭嘅機會</span></span><br />\n<br />\n最後 選擇唔出嘅 不了 覺得啲人好暴徒 fine 打到埋嚟 唔好怨 係你自己選擇 仆咗街 比個政府食住上 唔好喊  唔好後悔 因為 呢個係你<span style=\"font-size: large;\">姑息呢個政權嘅代價</span><br />\n<br />\n利申: 有衝  亦都同身邊嘅朋友、同事、家人 決定罷工 直至有一個香港人想要嘅結果為止"},{"pid":"e683067153ac3ae3e65c2712cd9fc1ac6d06591e","tid":1198900,"uid":15933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T10:56:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f89b3f292c0ffb6b757e4aa9b57d3ef1712b0d21","tid":1198900,"uid":15933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T10:56:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bb95f24af8268485593cf4b895da724d2b457eda","tid":1198900,"uid":15933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T10:57:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"909e5b33c80679a72d795c675ab1842d99467e4e","tid":1198900,"uid":15933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T10:57:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"226e30c5b36a8177937e020e3b54e94ab83fec2f","tid":1198900,"uid":15933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T10:57:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"aa5bf0815e453b74ed02e3dda048ce837da6625d","tid":1198900,"uid":20058,"like":14,"dislike":3,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T11:01:20.000Z","msg":"咁你知唔知琴日維園出發班友喺度乾蒸左幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我琴日去到金鐘已經冇力<br />\n唔係個個都有成本<br />\n利申三點半到維園<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4382a1014d421501d7624bf593af7ab5cb05ee61","tid":1198900,"uid":79278,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T11:05:49.000Z","msg":"怨個班友本身可能唔諗住出 <br />\n今次佢地肯出力出聲 只係無跟你衝 都要比你分化<br />\n下次連聲都無人出 你唔好開post怨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cebf01d3f9ed219406bb14684ea8f555e5765ab8","tid":1198900,"uid":217169,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T11:13:19.000Z","msg":"連登仔真係去又屌 唔去又屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"022ae455c928ab35d462576d150112d0de19a5c4","tid":1198900,"uid":55960,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T11:15:45.000Z","msg":"去又屌 唔去又屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有無諗過有D人身體狀況"},{"pid":"c60340c66dc2340a6205c43dd707527cc9ec8b4c","tid":1198900,"uid":15933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aa5bf0815e453b74ed02e3dda048ce837da6625d","tid":1198900,"uid":20058,"like":14,"dislike":3,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T11:01:20.000Z","msg":"咁你知唔知琴日維園出發班友喺度乾蒸左幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我琴日去到金鐘已經冇力<br />\n唔係個個都有成本<br />\n利申三點半到維園<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T11:18:34.000Z","msg":"兩點令去到維園<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都乾蒸咗好耐 <br />\n入咗黑我都唔知做緊乜"},{"pid":"6e41354df0546f86836e80212b243af430839268","tid":1198900,"uid":60545,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T11:18:35.000Z","msg":"唔係個個都有能力衝<br />\n不過希望大家聽晚/後朝再聚"},{"pid":"071ede9e0a69aa5c5028980cea298ca5e4b99ae3","tid":1198900,"uid":15933,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"4382a1014d421501d7624bf593af7ab5cb05ee61","tid":1198900,"uid":79278,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T11:05:49.000Z","msg":"怨個班友本身可能唔諗住出 <br />\n今次佢地肯出力出聲 只係無跟你衝 都要比你分化<br />\n下次連聲都無人出 你唔好開post怨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T11:22:39.000Z","msg":"點樣分化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我只係希望大家可以一齊出嚟 我都冇怨過真係有顧慮 有一家大細 or 學生<br />\n2014年我都做過係到怨嗰個 我只係覺得每個人都可以坐言起行就可以好似琴日咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"029e82ac49537edb4817417228a20e17bb765c77","tid":1198900,"uid":15933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6e41354df0546f86836e80212b243af430839268","tid":1198900,"uid":60545,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T11:18:35.000Z","msg":"唔係個個都有能力衝<br />\n不過希望大家聽晚/後朝再聚"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T11:24:51.000Z","msg":"係 但其實嗰晚有啲衝唔到 但都留咗係後面聲援<br />\n一有人比警察拉 後面啲人即刻影低同埋大力屌鳩啲狗"},{"pid":"a0015d03d6a061ec763c4017d79e3d9f80a57ccd","tid":1198900,"uid":15933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T11:27:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"716c4534d7bcf00f59bcc1d18fceec02b401f855","tid":1198900,"uid":145423,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T11:30:29.000Z","msg":"無辦法，自己真係唔敢沖，其實都唔想有人沖，一黎知道黑警步署好曬，睇海富出面就知，二黎果刻沖，唔會有咩作用，見到好多義士係龍和圍鐵馬，其實真係諗唔到意義係邊到，好似曾經係果到做過，就係番果到做，三黎真係唔想再見到有人要坐監/被打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a73a5e3860f45110e3cfa66e8f87ca3045f434df","tid":1198900,"uid":15933,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T11:41:59.000Z","msg":"係咪有啲人曲解我意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我唔係話返咗去唔衝就係衰人 <br />\n只係大家都肯再出嚟效果會好好多 而唔係喺到怨<br />\n琴晚都係衰流失咗好多人 但琴晚在場嘅人都好醒水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔衝嗰啲係面睇直播話比人聽成個金鐘點 邊都有狗 一批人救援 一批人比自己個眼罩人 一批人係天橋落唔到去都聲援樓下啲人/ 叫人避 一批人就衝 <br />\n同一比人捉就即刻衝去救人<br />\n<br />\n咁當然 返去嘅人就利用網絡 提供好多有用嘅資訊 因為在場好多冇leader  有小小唔知點 <br />\n不過好多在場嘅人都load唔到同追唔切po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <br />\n無論點 我只係希望多啲人出  形勢會好唔同的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"665488ff0fb5ccde28d48f6b9657ff15e334d7b7","tid":1198900,"uid":15933,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"716c4534d7bcf00f59bcc1d18fceec02b401f855","tid":1198900,"uid":145423,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T11:30:29.000Z","msg":"無辦法，自己真係唔敢沖，其實都唔想有人沖，一黎知道黑警步署好曬，睇海富出面就知，二黎果刻沖，唔會有咩作用，見到好多義士係龍和圍鐵馬，其實真係諗唔到意義係邊到，好似曾經係果到做過，就係番果到做，三黎真係唔想再見到有人要坐監/被打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T12:00:23.000Z","msg":"諒解的<br />\n其實無部署嘅衝 一味衝都唔係路 亦明白你覺得有風險嘅嘢唔係狂衝狂撞就有效果 相信都唔係全部人衝曬就做到圍堵 同埋相比警犬 琴晚實力幾懸殊下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但你有到好好了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />每個人在場至然會發揮佢嘅作用<br />\n幫手提供下資訊 遞水 就算影低到啲黑警都好好了<br />\n希望12號 你可以的話 都出嚟 唔好覺得自己好渺少<br />\n每個人都好重要 唔會真係多你一個唔多 少你一個唔少 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 11,12號見"},{"pid":"010a2e087499a6a3ed8b3db1fd83a3bb36c22ea5","tid":1198900,"uid":15933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T12:00:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8f86e81caf310a07582e025890c0a7a848c3d032","tid":1198900,"uid":15933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T12:00:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0b9040ce9e484d4cb28893200cd0a6f1c8ec195c","tid":1198900,"uid":15933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T12:00:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2a456c90507b58d9fea1dce841b5f3a0871af794","tid":1198900,"uid":15933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T12:01:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8cedc54688bc635cf7d81e6dd4ab630a3a3b59f4","tid":1198900,"uid":15933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T12:01:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"db94d5c1d5f7de52c39d033d4d93c420e5a23722","tid":1198900,"uid":15933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T12:01:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c27dd6d511bd3c4dc9b408e6b6ed7d50779fcb9d","tid":1198900,"uid":15933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T12:01:50.000Z","msg":"Pish"}]}